Detailed Description

A definition label.

Provides information on the word's field of interest, etc.

Equality, Hashing, and Copying

WNDefinitionLabel instances implement NSObject's hash and isEqual methods, as well as the NSCopying protocol. Instances may be compared by value using NSObject::isEqual: and may be used as a key in NSDictionary.
